While everyone has been obsessing over AI chatbots, a silent revolution has been happening in the physical world. The code has been given a body. This is the story of the new global arms race: the battle for the world's first true humanoid robot.

In this episode, we expose how Generative AI and LLMs have lit a fire under the robotics industry, transforming clunky machines into adaptable, intelligent beings. Hit play to witness the dawn of the robot age. After you listen, tell us in the comments: which strategy do you think will win—America's brain or China's brawn?
